      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BasicLine
      This enemy line has only simple enemies.
      class  Bullet
      This class creates "bullets" that will be shoot by the enemies or the player.

      This class creates an enemy to be added in the enemy line.
      class  EnemyLine
      This class gives the basic structure to all the enemy lines.
      class  LineClassA
      This enemy line has a boss and the entire line is destroyed if this enemy get destroyed.
      class  LineClassB
      This enemy line is similar to the class A, but the boss in this line will randomly change its position.
      class  LineClassC
      In this enemy line, when the boss die, another enemy takes its place as boss.
      class  LineClassD
      This enemy line order its enemies according to their resistance on a descending order.
      class  LineClassE
      This enemy line move its elements as a clock.
      class  Player
      This is the object that will be controlled by the user.
